        },
        "**Key properties:**",
        {
          "$ul": [
            "**applicationId**: The application identifier.<br><br><b>Endpoints</b>:<ul><li>POST cobrand/login</li></ul>",
            "**cobrandId**: Unique identifier of the cobrand (customer) in the system.<br><br><b>Endpoints</b>:<ul><li>POST cobrand/login</li></ul>",
            "**locale**: The customer's locale that will be considered for the localization functionality.<br><br><b>Endpoints</b>:<ul><li>POST cobrand/login</li></ul>",
            [
              "**session**",
              {
                "$ul": [
                  "**cobSession**"
                ]
              }
            ]
          ]
